\par }{\fs20\insrsid4065019 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 [to be added \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0  campaigning for a democratic secular republic - reference to republican people\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s Ch\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 arter initiative] 
\par 
